<item>
            <title>[QPID-3029] Java broker claims to support 2^16 channels per connection when it doesn&apos;t</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/QPID-3029</link>
                <project id="12310520" key="QPID">Qpid</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Java broker claims to support 2^16 channels per connection when it doesn&apos;t. It should negotiate the supported channel limit to the client during the protocol handshake.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
