                            <comment id="12990597" author="gemmellr" created="Fri, 4 Feb 2011 16:18:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Andrew can you review please? Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12996342" author="andrew.kennedy" created="Fri, 18 Feb 2011 10:49:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;In AMQP connections, the maximum number of channels is a two octet field. In ServerDelegate#getChannelMax() the number of channels should be 0xFFFF, not Integer.MAX_VALUE. Also, in Connection#map(Session) the loop through the channels map should start at Connection#MIN_USABLE_CHANNEL_NUM rather than explicitly using zero. These are not very important, and are trivial changes in any case.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12996343" author="andrew.kennedy" created="Fri, 18 Feb 2011 10:50:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Accepted changes&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
